data.title: Stage and Screen Stars Line up for New Woody Allen Film
data.meta_description: A host of actors have been announced for Woody Allen's currently untitled new film.
data.text:
EW.com reports that the starry cast will include Bruce Willis, Kristen Stewart, Stephen Kunken, Jesse Eisenberg, Blake Lively, Parker Posey, Jeannie Berlin, Corey Stoll, Ken Stott, Anna Camp, Sari Lennick and Paul Schneider.

No details have been revealed for the feature film. Shooting is scheduled to commence later this month in New York and Los Angeles.

Willis is scheduled to appear on Broadway this season in a 16-week engagement of the play Misery, which begins previews Oct. 22 and opens Nov. 15.

Oscar winner Allen is currently represented on screen by the new film "Irrational Man."
